HEADWORD: Horsy
<hw>Hors"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or
suggestive of, a horse, or of horse racing; <as>as, <ex>horsy</ex>
manners; garments of fantastically <ex>horsy</ex> fashions.</as></def>
